title: Bridget Moynahan Marries Andrew Frankel
text: Bridget Moynahan Marries Andrew Frankel Bridget Moynahan married businessman Andrew Frankel in New York over the weekend, ... Comment   TV Guide Posted Oct. 18, 2015 at 12:01 AM Updated Oct 18, 2015 at 10:09 PM By TV Guide Posted Oct. 18, 2015 at 12:01 AM Updated Oct 18, 2015 at 10:09 PM Bridget Moynahan married businessman Andrew Frankel in New York over the weekend, People reports. They tied the knot in an "intimate ceremony" in the Hamptons on Saturday evening. The couple were introduced through a mutual friend, according to People . Moynahan, who previously dated New England Patriots quarterback Tom Brady, has kept her relationship with Frankel - the co-president of a Wall Street brokerage firm - mostly out of the public spotlight. However, the Blue Bloods star did share a photo from their big day on Instagram: A photo posted by Bridget Moynahan (@bridgetmoynahan) on Oct 17, 2015 at 5:36pm PDT Moynahan shares a son, Jack, with Brady. Frankel also has three children. Other Links From TVGuide.com
